Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: White-collar unemployment
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wvw7
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Jul 1982
White-collar workers make up 'new unemployed' in recession-hit US. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less